-The current energy context is defined; A root-cause analysis, identification of bottlenecks and solutions to the NEEREA process (loan process to be adopted by the private sector) are proposed; Status of net-metering and Feed in Tariff (FiT) are defined and related policies with required legal and regulatory reforms adapted to the Lebanese context are developed based on experience (barriers and solutions) in other countries (Europe). 
